request.description:
Returns authorization-scoped list of all API endpoints the caller can access. The response includes endpoint paths, HTTP methods, and brief descriptions filtered by the caller's role and permissions.

Response format:
```json
{
  "endpoints": [
    {
      "path": "/api/v1/ssp_documents",
      "method": "GET",
      "description": "List SSP documents"
    }
  ]
}
```

Returns a paginated list of SSP documents scoped to the caller's authorization boundaries. Supports optional filtering by authorization_boundary_id and pagination via page/items query parameters.

Response format:
```json
{
  "ssp_documents": [...],
  "meta": { "total": 10, "page": 1, "items": 25 }
}
```

body.raw:
{
  "ssp_document": {
    "name": "ACME Cloud Platform SSP",
    "description": "System Security Plan for FedRAMP Moderate authorization of ACME Cloud Platform",
    "authorization_boundary_id": 1
  }
}

