request.description:
Returns all FedRAMP 20x KSI themes. Themes group related Key Security Indicators by security domain (e.g., AUTH for Authentication, VULN for Vulnerability Management).

Response format:
```json
{
  "themes": [
    {
      "code": "AUTH",
      "name": "Authentication",
      "description": "Identity and authentication controls",
      "indicators_count": 5
    }
  ]
}
```

Returns KSI indicators with optional filtering by theme and impact level. Indicators define specific measurable security outcomes required by FedRAMP 20x.

Response format:
```json
{
  "indicators": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "theme": "AUTH",
      "code": "AUTH-01",
      "name": "Multi-Factor Authentication",
      "impact_levels": ["low", "moderate", "high"],
      "nist_mappings_count": 3
    }
  ]
}
```

Returns a single KSI indicator by ID with full details including all NIST SP 800-53 control mappings. Shows which NIST controls satisfy this indicator.

Response format:
```json
{
  "indicator": {
    "id": 1,
    "theme": "AUTH",
    "code": "AUTH-01",
    "name": "Multi-Factor Authentication",
    "description": "System enforces MFA for all privileged and non-privileged users",
    "nist_mappings": [
      { "control_id": "ia-2", "relationship": "primary" },
      { "control_id": "ia-2(1)", "relationship": "supporting" }
    ]
  }
}
```

Returns the complete mapping table between FedRAMP 20x KSI indicators and NIST SP 800-53 controls. Useful for understanding which NIST controls contribute to each KSI.

Response format:
```json
{
  "mappings": [
    {
      "indicator_code": "AUTH-01",
      "nist_control_id": "ia-2",
      "relationship": "primary"
    }
  ]
}
```

